wikipedia_page.main: Zak William Seddon (born 28 June 1994) is an English runner specialising in the 3000 metres steeplechase. He competed for Great Britain but didn't make the finals of the 2017 World Championships. he won a gold medal at the 2013 European Junior Championships.
